## 4. Module Structure

```
beecon_app/lib/
├── main.dart                          # Bootstrap: dotenv, Hive, ProviderScope
├── core/
│   ├── constants/app_constants.dart   # Routes, keys, asset paths
│   ├── router/app_router.dart         # GoRouter + HomeShell bottom nav
│   ├── providers/destination_provider.dart  # Global navigation & map state
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── ors_service.dart           # OSRM (web) / ORS (mobile) polylines
│   │   └── gemini_service.dart        # AI accessibility + safety insights
│   ├── storage/
│   │   ├── hive_service.dart          # Hive boxes + connectivity check
│   │   └── ai_insight_storage.dart    # SharedPreferences AI banner
│   ├── theme/app_theme.dart
│   └── widgets/beecon_branding.dart
└── features/
    ├── auth/          # Splash, onboarding, mobility profile selection
    ├── home/          # Map, search, heatmaps, emergency, report tap mode
    ├── routing/       # Route models, scorers, results screen
    ├── reports/       # Community hazard reporting
    └── profile/       # User profile, saved locations
```

