    end

    subgraph MapControls["Controls"]
        SEARCH[LocationSearchPanel<br/>20 BGC destinations]
        TOGGLE[Heatmap Toggle<br/>Accessibility | Safety]
        REPORT[Report Tap Mode<br/>Red pin → bottom sheet]
        EMERG[Emergency FAB<br/>911 · BGC hotline · nearest security]
    end

    SEARCH --> PROV[Riverpod: origin, destination]
    PROV --> ROUTE
    TOGGLE --> HEAT
    REPORT --> MARKERS
    EMERG --> SEC_NAV[Navigate to nearest security post]
```

### Static BGC Data (`bgc_accessibility_data.dart`)

| Dataset | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `accessibilityFeatures` | Ramp, elevator, stairs, construction, tactile markers |
| `safetyZones` | Green / orange / red safety heatmap circles |
| `boundaryPolygon` | Map camera constraint |
| `searchDestinations` | Keyword → coordinate lookup |

