## 10. Community Reports Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    TAP[Map tap mode] --> PIN[Pending pin on map]
    PIN --> SHEET[ReportLocationSheet]
    SHEET --> FORM["/report?lat=&lng="]
    FORM --> HIVE[(Hive reports box)]
    HIVE --> MAP[Red triangle markers on Home map]
    MAP --> DETAIL[Tap marker → detail sheet]
```

Reports are **fully local** (Hive). No server sync in the current POC. Reports appear on the map for all sessions on the same device/browser profile.

---

## 11. State Management (Riverpod)

| Provider | Responsibility |
|----------|----------------|
| `currentGpsLocationProvider` | Device coordinates |
| `selectedOriginProvider` | Route origin (GPS or landmark) |
| `selectedDestinationProvider` | Route destination |
| `routePolylinesProvider` | OSRM/ORS polyline sets |
| `highlightedRouteTypeProvider` | Selected route line emphasis |
| `heatmapOverlayProvider` | `null` · `accessibility` · `safety` |
| `routesLoadingProvider` | ORS fetch in progress |
| `reportTapModeProvider` | Map tap reporting mode |
| `pendingReportPinProvider` | Unconfirmed report pin |
| `highlightReportLocationProvider` | Post-submit map focus |
| `originSearchQueryProvider` / `destinationSearchQueryProvider` | Search autocomplete |
| `canGetRoutesProvider` | Both endpoints set |

**Mobility profile** and onboarding completion use **SharedPreferences** via `AppConstants` keys (not Riverpod).

